{"word":"G3856 - παραδειγματίζω - paradeigmatízō - par-ad-igue-mat-id'-zo - Make a public example","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραδειγματίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paradeigmatízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ad-igue-mat-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Make a public example</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அவமானப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"expose to infamy, put to an open sham e"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G1165 - δειγματίζω - deigmatízō - digh-mat-id'-zo/1165\">G1165</a>; to <i>show alongside</i> (the public), that is, <i>expose to infamy:</i> - make a public example, put to an open shame.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1165/1165\">G1165</a>, <a href=\"#/G1166/1166\">G1166</a>, <a href=\"#/G322/322\">G322</a>, <a href=\"#/G323/323\">G323</a>, <a href=\"#/G3856/3856\">G3856</a>, <a href=\"#/G5262/5262\">G5262</a>"}]}